## Why this file exists

The user works across multiple devices and multiple AI tools (Claude Code on
desktop/laptop/phone, Windsurf on the work machine). They don't want to track
branches or remember tool-specific quirks. **Main = the user's computer.**
Every tool behaves identically: pull main at start, merge to main on save,
never ask about branches. This file guarantees Windsurf matches Claude Code.
